import { Grid, Typography } from '@mui/material'
import React from 'react'

export const TechnicalItem = ({ frontLanguage }) => {
   return (
      <Grid container direction="row" sx={{ fontFamily: "Noto Sans" }}>
         <Grid item>
            <Typography>Linguagem do front:</Typography>
         </Grid>
         <Grid item>
            <Typography>{frontLanguage}</Typography>
         </Grid>
      </Grid>
   )
}
